snippet.title: Three Reasons Jay-Z Didn't Perform With Beyonce At The Super Bowl
snippet.description: Beyoncé reunited at the Mercedes-Benz Superdome with Destiny’s Child mates Kelly Rowland and Michelle Williams, performing hits including “Bootylicious” and “Single Ladies.” Yet when she sang “Crazy In Love,” a song that features Jay-Z, the rapper was nowhere to be found.
